---

<section class="section" id="why-blogworms">
  <div class="container-blog">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-surface-900">Why Blog Worms?</h2>
      <p class="text-surface-600 mt-3 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        We're not just another blog — we're your daily dose of what's trending, explained clearly.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <!-- Pillar 1 -->
      <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-white hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-200 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          ⚡
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-surface-900 mb-2">Always Fresh</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-surface-600 leading-relaxed">
          We cover the latest UK trending topics as they break, giving you timely insights before anyone else.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pillar 2 -->
      <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-white hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-100 to-accent-200 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          🇬🇧
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-surface-900 mb-2">UK Focused</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-surface-600 leading-relaxed">
          Our content is tailored for UK audiences, covering topics that matter to readers across Britain.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pillar 3 -->
      <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-white hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-green-100 to-green-200 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          🔍
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-surface-900 mb-2">Deep Research</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-surface-600 leading-relaxed">
          We answer the questions Google hasn't, providing well-researched content you won't find elsewhere.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pillar 4 -->
      <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-white hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-100 to-purple-200 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          💡
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-surface-900 mb-2">Clear Writing</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-surface-600 leading-relaxed">
          No jargon, no fluff — just clear, engaging content that respects your time and intelligence.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
